                                                                        </p>
                                                                        <p class="moto-text_system_9"> <b>We would be honored to speak and pray with you.</b></p>
                                                                        <p><br><br></p>
                                                                        <p class="moto-text_system_10">Father there is nothing hidden from Your eye.  You saw our substance before we were formed in our mother’s womb.  Your word tells us that all our days were planned out and recorded before we were born.  You have a purpose and a plan for each of us, to prosper us and not harm us.  May we be opened to Your truth that You have already planned for us, and receive it, glorifying and honoring You. Let us ask this in the name of Jesus, Your Son.
                                                                        </p>
